</span>該兩名在選舉<span style=\"color: red;\">前</span>擔任<span style=\"color: red;\">正副主席</span>的委員<span style=\"color: red;\">均缺席或獲提名候選該職位，出席的其他委員中排名最先者須主持選舉</span>。如他獲提名候選該職位，在未獲提名的出席委員中排名最先者須主持選舉。"},{"pid":"0e2f8a691161007c24242fc340c195446765551c","tid":1977663,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38082be29d407136af792e2cc37bedf0f2426c35","tid":1977663,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"128c791b09affa9d7973224ccfd3b88d9bf8dc19","tid":1977663,"uid":22609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"琼子唔主持就會係涂謹申"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:40:05.000Z","msg":"咁拉鳩埋阿涂<br />\n保皇咪可以解決內會困局？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:47:20.000Z","msg":"再之後係梁耀忠、石禮謙<br />\n即係要同時拉郭榮鏗、涂謹申、梁耀忠"},{"pid":"91e48084c4a66f56f51d39839a1ff3e4b9b8e34e","tid":1977663,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7095b10921862310097e3413e09b255fded26411","tid":1977663,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f43c1780c56725ee9b53923370f1a9167266309c","tid":1977663,"uid":22609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"38082be29d407136af792e2cc37bedf0f2426c35","tid":1977663,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"128c791b09affa9d7973224ccfd3b88d9bf8dc19","tid":1977663,"uid":22609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"琼子唔主持就會係涂謹申"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:40:05.000Z","msg":"咁拉鳩埋阿涂<br />\n保皇咪可以解決內會困局？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"琼子主持就冇得選<br />\n剩返既候選人得飯民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:53:41.000Z","msg":"no 港共會做核突d<br />\n<br />\n叫琼子重啟選舉<br />\n<br />\n到時補番建制候選人"},{"pid":"5c6d5e06b744194cf67994495342ea111177